OL,3,CLeicester could scale back famous
OL,4,CDiwali celebrations due to financial
OL,5,Cproblems
OL,7,FLeicester's Diwali celebrations are
OL,8,Funder threat as the popular lights
OL,9,Fswitch-on could be scrapped this year.
OL,11,FEvery year 40,000 people flock to
OL,12,FBelgrave Road in Leicester for the
OL,13,Fbiggest Diwali celebrations outside of
OL,14,FIndia.
OL,16,FThe colourful festivities take place
OL,17,Fon two separate days, with the lights
OL,18,Fswitch-on followed by Diwali Day two
OL,19,Fweeks later.
