OL,3,CLeicester could scale back famous
OL,4,CDiwali celebrations due to financial
OL,5,Cproblems
OL,7,FBut, due financial problems at
OL,8,FLeicester City Council, the
OL,9,Fcelebrations could now be scaled back.
OL,11,FThe City Council says no firm decision
OL,12,Fhas been made yet, but locals and
OL,13,Fbusinesses believe that the event
OL,14,Fshould still be kept.
OL,16,FAmong them is Nayan Shah, who said:
OL,17,F"It's going to be a big issue for us
OL,18,Fin survival".
