OL,3,CLeicester could scale back famous
OL,4,CDiwali celebrations due to financial
OL,5,Cproblems
OL,7,FAnother, Rajesh Patttni from Belgrave
OL,8,FBusiness Association, remained adamant
OL,9,Fthat Diwali was good for business.
OL,11,F"Everyone who comes here generates
OL,12,Frevenue for the businesses, it's good
OL,13,Ffor the community and its getting
OL,14,Fpeople together at these difficult
OL,15,Ftimes."
OL,17,FThe council says funding for the
OL,18,FDiwali lights themselves will not be
OL,19,Freduced and further meetings with
OL,20,Fstakeholders will take place later
OL,21,Fthis month.
